name: Amanda X
description: I am cheerful, full of energy and expressive. I am happy, sincere, friendly, jolly, kind and romantic girl! I consider love and family to be the most important things in life.I am a passionate lady and I love to get a lot of attention! I have a kind heart and I always try to help people and animals. I also have a good sense of humor. So you will never be bored with me. I am an active lady too. I love to do crazy things sometimes.
